OL,5, New teachers are abandoning the        
OL,6, profession because they are not being  
OL,7, offered secure jobs, Scotland's largest
OL,8, teaching union has said.               
OL,10,FThe Educational Institute of Scotland  
OL,11,F(EIS) said many newly-qualified staff  
OL,12,Fwere only being given short contracts. 
OL,14,FThe union is urging the Scottish       
OL,15,Fgovernment to increase council funding 
OL,16,Fto pay for more permanent jobs.        
OL,18,FThe Scottish government said it was    
OL,19,F"taking strong action" to protect      
OL,20,Fincreased teacher numbers.             
